testimonials.testimonial: Alicia is an absolute pleasure to work with. She is incredibly kind, fun, and accommodating, and she has extensive knowledge of all things related to weddings, not just photography! Every photo she takes is a work of art.

Alicia was amazing! We had her for 6 hours for our wedding day and she captured so much in such a short amount of time. The photos capture us as a couple, us with our friends, and us with our families so perfectly.
Alicia made our engagement and wedding photos a breeze and they are something we will treasure for the rest of our lives! She made us much more comfortable in front of the camera.

Alicia took our maternity photos and came to our home to take newborn photos as well. She was absolutely amazing to work with, and after an especially long journey to have a baby we will treasure these photos forever!

Alicia photographed our tiny, intimate wedding right around the holidays. She was responsive and helpful during the booking process and took time to understand our vision. The magic really happened on the day— she did an AMAZING job executing our vision!

Alicia has that rare talent of capturing the true essence of a moment while making it all look effortless. We love Alicia so much!! My husband and I both hate having our photo taken but Alicia helps us feel at ease and guides our poses.

If you want a photographer that won’t ask your reluctant family photo attendee to do anything stupid - Alicia is your girl! She jumped right in to snapping photos of the non-stop energy that is three little boys that have no chill.
